Interface HedwigModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ModelReadOnly, ModelUpdate
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Model
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface HedwigModel
extends ModelUpdate, ModelReadOnly
    Instances of this interface represent the state of some OWL+SWRL model. The methods in this interface are called by the API generated by the Hedwig tool.
